title: BBC Britains Greatest Pilot The Extraordinary Story of Captain W
description:
Britain's Greatest Pilot (BBC)

Biography Documentary hosted by James Holland, published by BBC in 2014 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/0/01/Britain-s-Greatest-Pilot-BBC-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Captain Eric 'Winkle' Brown recounts his flying experiences, encounters with the Nazis and other adventures leading up to and during the Second World War. Illustrated with archive footage and Captain Brown's own photos.
